title: What do you do in matches like these?
body:
http://matchhistory.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/#match-details/NA1/1625577325/212856744

My team was full of cowards and never wanted to initiate first which lead us to a loss since the enemy team got all their ults off perfectly at the very end.

I seriously do not know how you're supposed to win these kinds of matches, because I got extremely fed, I roamed, and helped my team, yet Nasus and Lee Sin carried their team to victory, which is irritating because everyone else on their team did terrible until lategame comes around then everyone is pretty much at full builds so doing bad doesn't matter since you already have everything you need.

I really don't know what else I could have done as I tried everything to carry yet it wasn't enough, but perhaps you guys have some advice?
